  "derive": null,
  "notes": "Table A-8 (page 44) is the Total City average-salary-by-age-and-service exhibit; Table A-7 (page 44) provides the corresponding member counts used as weights for merging finer bins. The printed 'Avg. Salary' row and 'Total' column of Table A-8 are averages, not sums, so they cannot be validated against cell sums and are set to null. The counts table (Table A-7) prints true additive totals, which are transcribed. Target age bucket '70' merges source rows '65 to 69' and '70 and up'; target service bucket '4' merges 'Under 1' + '1 to 4' and bucket '40' merges '35 to 39' + '40 and up' - all via weighted_avg using counts. Empty cells shown as '-' in the source are transcribed as null."
